title: Pixle 2 to 4a
content: Trying to set up new pixle 4a. I have a pixle 2. All are updated charged and working properly. When I plug In the cable it says cable can't transfer data. I've tried the brand new cord my pixle 2 cord and 5 others. All it will do is charge between the 2 devices. It's set to file transfer by default but it will not
